'''盖伊·武夫·川崎'''（{{lang-en|Guy Takeo Kawasaki}}<ref>{{cite web |url= https://privatefunddata.com/fund-employees/guy-takeo-kawasaki-3082972/ |title= Guy Takeo Kawasaki – Garage Technology Ventures, LLC |publisher= PrivateFUNDData |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2019-03-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190330221533/https://privatefunddata.com/fund-employees/guy-takeo-kawasaki-3082972/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>，{{bd|1954年|8月30日||}}），美国市场营销专家、作家、[[硅谷|硅谷]][[风险投资|风险投资家]]<ref name=Cameron2010>{{cite news |title= Weekend Reading: Guy Kawasaki Author Spotlight |url= http://readwrite.com/2010/02/26/weekend-reading-guy-kawasaki |publisher= ReadWrite |first= Chris |last= Cameron |date= 2010-02-26 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2019-03-31 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190331021644/https://readwrite.com/2010/02/26/weekend-reading-guy-kawasaki/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。他是[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]最早的员工之一，负责1984年推出的[[麥金塔|麥金塔]]计算机产品线的市场营销。在推广工作中，他将麦金塔宣传为“{{le|苹果传播者|Apple evangelist}}”，从总体上提出了{{tsl|en|evangelism marketing|传播者营销}}和[[技术传播者|技术传播者]]（或称{{le|平台传播者|platform evangelism}}）的理念，普及了“传播者”这一概念<ref>{{cite book |last1=K. Breakenridge |first1=Deirdre |last2=Solis |first2=Brian |title=Putting the Public Back in Public Relations: How Social Media Is Reinventing the Aging Business of PR |date=2009-02-19 |publisher=FT Press |page=9 |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=xLXinA8LbTMC&pg=PA9&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false |access-date=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2021-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514135509/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=xLXinA8LbTMC&pg=PA9&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title= Technology Evangelists: A Leadership Survey |url= https://www.gri.co/pub/res/pdf/TechEvangelist.pdf |format= [[可移植文档格式|PDF]] |publisher= Growth Resources, Inc. |first= Frederic |last= Lucas-Conwell |date= 2006-12-04 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2017-03-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170313050630/https://www.gri.co/pub/res/pdf/TechEvangelist.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2015年3月到2016年12月担任[[维基百科|维基百科]]非盈利运营实体[[维基媒体基金会|维基媒体基金会]]的董事会成员<ref name="Henner">{{cite web |url= https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Foundation_Board_noticeboard/December_2016_-_Update_regarding_expiring_Board_terms |title= Update regarding expiring Board terms |last= Henner |first= Christophe |date= 2016-12-23 |publisher= Wikimedia Foundation |accessdate= 2017-01-12 |archive-date= 2017-01-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170113154748/https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Foundation_Board_noticeboard/December_2016_-_Update_regarding_expiring_Board_terms |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

川崎曾撰写多本著作，包括《{{le|麦金塔之道|The Macintosh Way}}》（1990）、《创业的艺术》（2004）和《Wise Guy》（2019）。

==早年==
盖伊·川崎生于[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]][[檀香山|檀香山]]，父亲为杜克·武·川崎（{{lang|en|Duke Takeshi Kawasaki}}，2015年卒），母亲为川崎爱子（{{lang|en|Aiko Kawasaki}}）<ref>{{cite web |url= http://obits.staradvertiser.com/2015/09/16/duke-takeshi-kawasaki/ |title= Duke Takeshi Kawasaki |date= 2015-09-16 |publisher= Star-Advertiser |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2019-03-31 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190331042747/https://obits.staradvertiser.com/2015/09/16/duke-takeshi-kawasaki/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://m.sfgate.com/news/article/Guy-Kawasaki-a-doting-father-and-hockey-player-3639773.php |title= Guy Kawasaki a doting father - and hockey player |date= 2012-06-17 |work= SFGate |last= Evangelista |first= Benny |access-date= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2019-03-31 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190331042606/https://m.sfgate.com/news/article/Guy-Kawasaki-a-doting-father-and-hockey-player-3639773.php |dead-url= no }}</ref>。全家人住在檀香山城外的{{tsl|en|Kalihi|卡利希谷}}。杜克曾当过消防员、房地产经纪、州参议员和公务员，爱子则是家庭主妇<ref>{{cite web |url= https://guykawasaki.com/to_build_a_case/ |title= A Brief History of Mine |website= guykawasaki.com |access-date= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2021-10-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211014093942/https://guykawasaki.com/to_build_a_case/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。1972年，川崎从[[伊奥拉尼書院|伊奥拉尼書院]]毕业<ref name=about>{{cite web |url= http://guykawasaki.com/guy-kawasaki |title= Who Is Guy? |website= guykawasaki.com |first= Guy |last= Kawasaki |date= 2015 |access-date= 2015-08-09 |archive-date= 2015-08-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150815035518/http://guykawasaki.com/guy-kawasaki/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

1976年，川崎凭[[心理学|心理学]][[文学士|文学士]]学位从[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]毕业<ref name=about/>，之后负笈至[[加利福尼亞大學戴維斯分校|加利福尼亞大學戴維斯分校]][[法学院|法学院]]，但由于不适应法律课程，仅上了一个星期的课便辍学<ref>{{cite av media |url= https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HHjgK6p4nrw |first= Guy |last= Kawasaki |title= The Top 10 Mistakes of Entrepreneurs |date= 2013-03-11 |format= Video |work= YouTube |access-date= 2015-08-09 |archive-date= 2015-08-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150824031647/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HHjgK6p4nrw |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= Iwata |first= Edward |url= http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/money/companies/management/entre/2008-11-09-nononina-guy-kawasaki_N.htm |title= Entrepreneur Guy Kawasaki Doesn't Accept Failure |date= 2008-11-10 |work= USA Today |access-date= 2015-08-09 |archive-date= 2016-03-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305064020/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/money/companies/management/entre/2008-11-09-nononina-guy-kawasaki_N.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。1977年，他就读于[[加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校|加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校]][[安德森管理学院|安德森管理学院]]，获[[工商管理硕士|工商管理硕士]]<ref name=about/>。在管理学院期间，川崎还供职于珠宝公司新型造型（{{lang|en|Nova Stylings}}）。他观察到：“珠宝行业非常非常艰难，比计算机行业还要艰难......我学到非常有价值的一堂课：如何销售<ref>{{cite news |last= Bryant |first= Adam |url= https://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/21/business/21corner.html?smid=pl-share |title= Just Give Him 5 Sentences, Not 'War and Peace' |work= The New York Times |date= 2010-03-10 |access-date= 2015-08-09 |archive-date= 2021-08-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210812161007/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/21/business/21corner.html?smid=pl-share |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”

==生涯==
{{external media |width=210px |align= right |header=盖伊·川崎演讲 | video1=[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mtjatz9r-Vc 创新的艺术] 盖伊·川崎，TEDx伯克利，[[TED大会|TEDx大会]]，21:15，2014年2月22日 |video2=[https://vimeo.com/75996729 你在社交媒体上很少听到的10个词]，社交数据周，2013年9月16日，29:21 |accessdate= 2015-03-25 }}

1983年，川崎在斯坦福室友{{le|迈克·伯奇|Mike Boich}}的引荐下加入[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]<ref name=about/><ref name=successmagazine>{{cite web |last= Ostdick |first= John |url= http://www.success.com/article/guy-kawasaki-advice-for-making-your-venture-successful |title= Guy Kawasaki: Advice for Making Your Venture Successful |website= success.com |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2016-12-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161207060807/http://www.success.com/article/guy-kawasaki-advice-for-making-your-venture-successful |dead-url= no }}</ref>，接下来四年内担任苹果的[[技术传播者|首席传播官]]。2006年接受“企业之声”（{{lang|en|Venture Voice}}）播客采访时，川崎透露：“我离开的主要原因是我开始听自己的一番炒作，便产生了要开一家软件公司真正赚大钱的念头<ref name=venturevoice>{{cite web |last= Galant |first= Greg |url= http://www.venturevoice.com/2006/10/vv_show_39_guy_kawasaki_of_gar.html |title= VW Show #39 – Guy Kawasaki of Garage Technology Ventures |website= venturevoice.com |date= 2006-10-16 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2017-07-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170703020247/http://www.venturevoice.com/2006/10/vv_show_39_guy_kawasaki_of_gar.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”1987年，他出任法国ACI美国分公司ACIUS的主管，该公司曾为苹果发布了数据库软件系统{{le|第4维|4th Dimension （software)}}<ref>{{cite news |last= Brogan |first= Daniel |url= http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1987-07-12/business/8702200992_1_macintosh-program-4th-dimension-users-group |title= Seeking 4th Dimension? Take Heart, Its Now in Town |newspaper= The Chicago Tribune |date= 1987-07-12 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2012-05-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120513111906/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1987-07-12/business/8702200992_1_macintosh-program-4th-dimension-users-group |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

1989年，川崎离开ACIUS，开始写作和演讲事业。1990年代早期，他担任《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》和《{{tsl|en|MacUser|MacUser}}》杂志的专栏作家<ref name=about/><ref>{{cite web |last=Kawasaki |first=Guy |url=https://www.forbes.com/forbes/1997/0825/6004084a.html |title=The Beauty of Metaphor |website=Forbes |date=August 25, 1997 |accessdate=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330233448/https://www.forbes.com/forbes/1997/0825/6004084a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last= Kawasaki |first= Guy |url= http://www.macworld.com/article/135883/1993/08/kawasaki_phone.html |title= Wise Guy: The Goal of a New Machine |publisher= Macworld |date= 2003-08-11 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2008-12-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20081207014903/http://www.macworld.com/article/135883/1993/08/kawasaki_phone.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。他还成立了Fog City Software公司，创造了{{tsl|en|Claris|Claris}}的邮件客户端{{tsl|en|Claris Emailer|Emailer}}<ref>{{cite web |url= http://tidbits.com/article/1539 |title= Emailer Licensed to Claris |work= TidBITS |date= 1995-04-03 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2017-02-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170223014634/http://tidbits.com/article/1539 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name=furchgott>{{citation |last= Furchgott |first= Roy |title= Private Sector; Financier to the Garage Start-Up |newspaper= The New York Times |date= 1998-10-18 |url= https://www.nytimes.com/1998/10/18/business/private-sector-financier-to-the-garage-start-up.html?src=pm |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2019-03-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190330233333/https://www.nytimes.com/1998/10/18/business/private-sector-financier-to-the-garage-start-up.html?src=pm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。1990年代，盖伊·川崎冠名的《盖伊实用软件集》（{{lang|en|''Guy's Utilities for Macintosh''}}）由After Hours Software发布<ref>{{cite web |title= More Utilities, By GUM |last= Engst |first= Adam C. |work= TidBITS |date= 1992-05-18 |url= https://tidbits.com/1992/05/18/more-utilities-by-gum/ |accessdate= 2018-06-02 |archive-date= 2019-03-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190330233435/https://tidbits.com/1992/05/18/more-utilities-by-gum/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。[[PowerBook|PowerBook]]版的工具集被{{tsl|en|Gordon Eubanks|戈登·尤班克斯}}买下，随后被[[赛门铁克|赛门铁克]]以《诺顿PowerBook必备软件》（{{lang|en|''The Norton Essentials for PowerBook''}}）的名义重新推出<ref>{{cite web |title= CPU |last= Engst |first= Adam C. |publisher= TidBITS |date= 1992-08-10 |url= https://tidbits.com/1992/08/10/cpu/ |accessdate= 2018-06-02 |archive-date= 2019-03-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190330233302/https://tidbits.com/1992/08/10/cpu/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Computer Age 5 |work=The Age |via=Newspapers |date=1993-02-09 |page=36 |location=Melbourne, Australia |url=https://www.newspapers.com/newspage/120467508/ |accessdate=2018-06-02 |archive-date=2018-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181122143253/https://www.newspapers.com/newspage/120467508/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1995年，川崎重返苹果<ref name=about/>。1998年担任[[风险投资|风险投资]]公司车库技术投资（{{lang|en|Garage Technology Ventures}}），投资了[[Pandora电台|Pandora电台]]、{{tsl|en|Tripwire （company)|Tripwire}}、{{tsl|en|The Motley Fool|The Motley Fool}}和D.light Design<ref name=alltop>{{cite web|last=Ostdick |first=John |url=http://www.successmagazine.com/guy-kawasaki-advice-from-an-apple-veteran/PARAMS/article/916 |title=Guy Kawasaki: Advice for Making Your Business Successful |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110924025504/http://www.successmagazine.com/guy-kawasaki-advice-from-an-apple-veteran/PARAMS/article/916 |archivedate=2011-09-24 |website=Success Magazine}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= Pritchard |first= Stephen |url= https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/analysis-and-features/guy-kawasaki-the-garage-culture-comes-to-britain-694099.html |title= Guy Kawasaki: The garage culture comes to Britain |newspaper= The Independent |date= 2000-08-28 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2019-03-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190330233345/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/analysis-and-features/guy-kawasaki-the-garage-culture-comes-to-britain-694099.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2007年成立了自由流动流言传播网站{{tsl|en|Truemors|Truemors}}，之后将其卖给了{{tsl|en|NowPublic|NowPublic}}<ref>{{cite news |last= Arrington |first= Michael |url= https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/07/10/AR2008071000900.html |title= Guy Kawasaki's Truemors Gets Acquired by NowPublic |newspaper= Washington Post |date= 2008-07-10 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2021-05-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210514135756/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/07/10/AR2008071000900.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.asianweek.com/2008/07/01/apple-evangelist%e2%80%99s-advice-for-silicon-valley-entrepreneurs/ |title= Apple Evangelist's Advice For Silicon Valley Entrepreneurs |newspaper=Asian Week |date= 2008-07-01 |access-date= 2008-07-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080803074329/http://www.asianweek.com/2008/07/01/apple-evangelist%E2%80%99s-advice-for-silicon-valley-entrepreneurs/ |archive-date= 2008-08-03 |dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.thebusinessmakers.com/episodes/shows/2007/june/episode-104/guy-kawasaki-truemors.html |title= Guy Kawasaki: Truemors and the $12,000 start-up |website= thebusinessmakers.com |date= 2007-06-02 |accessdate= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2009-05-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090526081200/http://www.thebusinessmakers.com/episodes/shows/2007/june/episode-104/guy-kawasaki-truemors.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。另外还创办了杂志网站[[Alltop|Alltop]]<ref name=successmagazine/><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.itworld.com/guy-kawasaki-interview-p1-080401/ |title= Interview: Not Just an Experiment: Guy Kawasaki's Alltop.com |website= itworld.com |date=2008-04-01 |dead-url= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110713070626/http://www.itworld.com/guy-kawasaki-interview-p1-080401/ |archivedate= 2011-07-13  }}</ref>。

2013年3月，川崎加入[[Google|Google]]，担任[[摩托罗拉|摩托罗拉]]顾问，打造[[Google+|Google+]]移动版<ref>{{cite web |url= http://readwrite.com/2013/03/01/google-disses-motorola-products-and-hires-guy-kawasaki |title= Google Disses Motorola Products - And Hires Guy Kawasaki |work= ReadWrite |date= 2013-03-01 |access-date= 2020-08-06 |archive-date= 2021-02-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210226104707/https://readwrite.com/2013/03/01/google-disses-motorola-products-and-hires-guy-kawasaki/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

